      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup by a second analyst; checklist-based verification of boundary conditions and material assignments.",
      "rationale": "A second qualified analyst independently reviewed the model setup, boundary conditions, and material property assignments against the documented simulation plan. No discrepancies were identified. Required level 2 is satisfied."
