      "acceptanceCriteria": "Linear elastic model with frictional contact is appropriate for the pre-yield loading regime targeted by the three QoIs.",
      "rationale": "The three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) are dominated by elastic deformation and contact mechanics. A linear elastic constitutive model with Coulomb friction at the screw-block interface is well-established for this loading regime. Sensitivity analyses confirm model form uncertainty is bounded within acceptance criteria."
