      "rationale": "Material elastic modulus and yield strength were taken from certified material test reports for the actual screw lot. Geometry was derived from CMM measurements of three representative screws, with dimensional tolerances propagated through a sensitivity analysis. Input uncertainty is quantified and within acceptable bounds."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
