      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions should span the range of clinically relevant loading rates and construct configurations to adequately characterize model fidelity across the COU.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single standardized ASTM F1717 loading configuration at a fixed displacement rate of 5 mm/min. The protocol is well-established and broadly accepted for regulatory submissions. Inter-laboratory reproducibility was confirmed with coefficient of variation below 5% across both sites, demonstrating robust experimental control."
    },
